    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 You have to see this absolute beauty! It's basically brand new and has been pampered like a member of the family since day one. Seriously, it\u2019s in flawless shape\u2014not a scratch on it and it still has that fresh car smell. I honestly hate to part with it, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. It drives like a dream, so come take it for a spin! You won\u2019t be disappointed! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1995 Mazda RX-7 FD3S. This example features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with sequential twin-turbochargers that deliver a seamless transition and robust boost pressure throughout the rev range. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the engine displays excellent compression across all rotor faces, and the cooling system has been proactively addressed with an uprated aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential for precise lateral grip and corner-exit stability. Finished in its factory-original paint with a pristine interior devoid of any dash warping or bolster wear, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking a mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless rotary icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service history. No cosmetic or mechanical flaws. Clean title.",
      "price": 46000.0,
