    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly collector-grade specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presented in showroom condition. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent persists. Every switch, dial, and electronic system operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been maintained exclusively by authorized technicians with a complete, chronological service binder included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Serious inquiries only for this investment-quality piece.",
      "price": 44500.0,
